metadata.name: Wac-A-Apple
metadata.description:
Created December 6th ,2021 ! This Adam & Eve inspired piece all started as a tree , And slowly developed and got inspired by a Wac-A-Mole arcade game. This piece in particular set the tone for anything and everything I made after it, After making this I took advantage of the zone flow I was in. 

3000px x 3000px
300 DPI
Edition 1/1
